Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's this boy I'd like to meet,\Nnamed Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is he in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A First Rendezvous of Tears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've finally found you!\NAsuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,H... hey, what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I looked all over town for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It took so long to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:46.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess I couldn't find you,\Nsince you're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:49.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Answer my question,\Nbefore this turns into a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:53.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's a new student!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess she doesn't need me\Nto take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:04.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:09.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cute... cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Relax. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Rina Takamiya"\NI'm Rina Takamiya,\Na new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, why don't you show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:30.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:34.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why not?! You should be\Nnice to new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's cool, I like tall girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:38.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:40.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's got a nice figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You over there!\NDon't go making assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She heard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm going to\Nbecome a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NI'm going to catch bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:04.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Especially that sneaky thief,\NSt. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to arrest her with\Nmy bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's going\Nto arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:16.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ms. Takamiya, Asuka Jr. was\Nappointed by the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,to investigate St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, the Mayor happens\Nto be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Mayor's Niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right?\NIs... that... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go right over and ask\Nmy Uncle for permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail won't be captured\Nthat easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing, you're trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's with her,\Nsticking so close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Suit yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:52.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ancient Hidden Treasures Exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's being held now\Nat the Central Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:04.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The "Dagger of Yatto"\Nthat's on display...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,is not what it seems to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not a hidden treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The dagger is a copy\Nthat I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a replica!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Replica... you mean it's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I usually work as a sculptor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But one day, I was asked by the man\Nin charge of Central Hall, Mr. Mizutani...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,to make a replica of the\NDagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:42.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I made it because he promised me that\Nhe was only going to use it as...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,a decoration in his house,\Njust to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I never thought he would exhibit it\Nas the real Dagger of Yatto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If I report it to the police,\NI'll probably be arrested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:58.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep at night because I think\Nabout everybody I'm deceiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Lord will surely forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've confessed\Nand repented.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm sure the Lord\Nwill guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So that's the story, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about\Nancient relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,whether it's Jomon period earthenware,\Na burial mound figure, or a clay doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,you can count on\NSt. Tail to recover it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,it's a dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea of how things are\Nbetween you and Ms. Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,but try to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, I'm quite sure my magic\Ntrick will work this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:18.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not right now. But, could I\Nborrow one of your magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One of my magic tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:31.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to send him a warning\Nthat will blow his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!\NCan I eat lunch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No way!\NGirls always want to trade snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to Central Hall tonight\Nto get the Dagger of Yatto..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:03.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,For a thief, she sure does send\Nlovely warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:04.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let me taste some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey don't eat it!\NIt's my lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NDon't hog it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Hey don't eat my hand!\N-Let go!!\NWhat is with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Your chopsticks broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My name is Mizutani and I'm the\None in charge of this exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is mine, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's get down to business.\NMay I see the Dagger of Yatto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a movie set.\NAll this justfor the exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:10.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I even have a special exhibition\Nroom just for the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:22.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's inside this pyramid set.\NWe've set up a room in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:30.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If the dagger is stolen and\Nthere's an investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:46.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The cameras are on 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:52.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are there any particular orders\Nyou have for the guards on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shall we guard it\Nfrom inside the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No... just guard the entrance\Nof the exhibition hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:09.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll hide inside that Sarcophagus,\Nif it's ok with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:16.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail usually appears from above.\NSo this should give me a good view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'll make her think this place\Nis not heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,When she comes in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch her in the act and\Narrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This set is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The place is narrow, so I'll get\Nher for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not clever enough, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You've got to trap her\Nmore aggressively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:46.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're bothering me,\Nso go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... You really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wh... what?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"To Askua Jr. ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:58.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Please look after my niece, Rina.\NI'm sure she'll be able to help you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Please let her assist you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:02.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mayor Hideo Morinaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:11.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the surveillance room,\Nwatching for your strategy to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:19.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But with my strategy, tonight will be\Nthe last night for St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who said that you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Read... Read...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Especially for Ms. Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose tonight's fight.\NThey will see my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They're only guarding the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty lenient, considering\Nthey're up against St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Dagger of Yatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rina, the security camera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen at\Nsuch a critical moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please Stand By.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's here...\NSt. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right, as soon as you touch\Nthat case, you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's got to be kidding,\Nnot taking us seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't count on Asuka's strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Set target: Inside the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, it'll all be over in a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There, now the gas will\Nfill the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape now, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Try not to... breathe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He'll see my face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get out of here!\NTake it easy Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But... I can 't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to flee, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's no use... I can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:39.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My eyes are so teary,\NI can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:45.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tear gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It should have worked by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he doing with her?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!\NWhere is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There couldn't have been a better\Nopportunity to catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:17.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! "What were you doing!"\Nis something I should be asking you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:20.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Killed you, my foot!\NYou two were hugging each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rina! The Dagger of Yatto\Nhas been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm taking\Nthe dagger with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Mr. Detective.\NIt's been fun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She did it again, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Show me you face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, what do you think\Nyou're looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Stupid! Super Stupid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We could've caught her,\Nif you held onto her tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have to use\Ntear gas to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who will capture\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself! Humph!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:52.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:11.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I left security for this place\Nup to him because he's your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I trusted him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how valuable the\NDagger of Yatto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,both as an archeological\Nand artistic treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's so valuable, that no monetary\Nvalue could be placed on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How are the police going to take\Nresponsibility for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's a nice painting.\NDon't tell me this is an imitation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've already investigated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:40.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I hear that your Dagger of Yatto\Nis a genuine replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Getting the police involved\Nin your conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,that's taking it a bit too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"IT WAS A FAKE!"\NWhat a stupid thief,\Nstealing a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She ends up stealing for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:12.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She probably was helping\Nsomebody out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And just how would you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,because I've been chasing\Nher all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, I'll reveal your\Ntrue identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You were crying last night,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,'Cause your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why did you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Men have a lot things to\Nattend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:07.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know, it's because you're always\Ndedicated to the job you 're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're kind.
